WEBVTT

00:00.272 --> 00:02.282
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:02.307 --> 00:04.749
I don't know what
your alien friends did to you,

00:04.774 --> 00:07.023
but I for one
do not want to find out.

00:07.048 --> 00:08.773
We are fighting
the same enemy.

00:08.930 --> 00:10.355
If the rebellion
isn't real,

00:10.380 --> 00:12.134
then nothing that's happened
makes any sense.

00:12.159 --> 00:13.982
If the Skitters are gonna
overthrow their Masters...

00:14.007 --> 00:15.804
Maybe it could be true.

00:15.829 --> 00:17.175
Look, I don't know
what you're plotting,

00:17.200 --> 00:19.271
but I'd rather swallow glass
than be a part of it.

00:19.296 --> 00:20.523
Charleston

00:20.623 --> 00:22.737
We've been promised
paradise before

00:22.762 --> 00:24.425
There's no way to know for sure.

00:24.450 --> 00:25.421
Who goes there?

00:25.446 --> 00:27.562
Colonel Porter,
First Continental Army.

00:27.587 --> 00:29.318
Let's go to Charleston.

00:32.677 --> 00:34.344
Can't tell you
how proud I am

00:34.379 --> 00:36.245
of the way you guys kept
the 2nd Mass in the fight.

00:36.279 --> 00:38.514
Last we heard, your unit
was taking some pretty heavy fire.

00:38.548 --> 00:40.414
Yeah, Mechs
tore the hell out of us.

00:40.448 --> 00:42.949
We put up a fight, but in the end,
only five survived.

00:42.984 --> 00:45.217
All we could do
was patch up the wounded,

00:45.252 --> 00:47.620
bury the dead, and try
to make our way down here.

00:52.425 --> 00:54.459
We're basically
in a defensive posture,

00:54.494 --> 00:55.895
just staying off
the alien grid.

00:55.929 --> 00:57.864
How'd anyone
even find this place?

00:57.898 --> 00:59.198
Dumb luck.

00:59.233 --> 01:00.333
This place
was under construction

01:00.368 --> 01:01.535
when they hit the city.

01:01.570 --> 01:03.672
Everything topside
was destroyed.

01:03.707 --> 01:07.243
Everything down below...
survived.

