01:23.929 --> 01:26.330
Oh, my God.

01:43.950 --> 01:46.953
What the hell
they staring at?

02:01.437 --> 02:03.438
2nd Mass, welcome!

02:06.576 --> 02:09.412
Looks like your reputation
precedes you, folks.

02:09.446 --> 02:11.414
Welcome to Charleston.

02:14.852 --> 02:16.320
Happy to have you!

02:25.098 --> 02:29.098
